import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './pages/Home/'


ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Router>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Home />} />
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  </React.StrictMode>
)

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot()
root.render(
    <React.StrictMode>
        <Home />
    </React.StrictMode>
)
